  <tr>
    <td width colspan="3" align="left" rowspan="7" valign="top"><font face="Verdana">
    <p>This item when equiped, will allow a mage to summon a larger pet, this pet seems to have more HP's, but the attack remains the same.  It can be used as a magic weapon.</p>
<p>
This is a quest given by " Vira " in the Temple of RO.  Quest items are a shovel ( from najena, or croc's in Cazic ), Ruby, Gargoyle eye, HG toes.</p>
STR: +3, INT: +2<br>
NO DROP
		
		</font></td>
    
  
	 	
  </tr>
